convertXDL2NMC

public static java.lang.String convertXDL2NMC(java.lang.String xdlFileName)
Converts the file called xdlFileName to an NMC with a file by the same name but with an .nmc extension. Note that this will always have 1 error with Virtex 4 parts as they will never contain all DCMs configured. This error can be ignored.

Parameters:
xdlFileName - The XDL file to convert.
Returns:
Name of the output NMC file.

convertXDL2NCD

Converts xdlFileName to an NCD file called ncdFileName. It uses the -force option by default

Parameters:
xdlFileName - The input XDL file
ncdFileName - The output NCD file
